        "content": "## 🔑 Credentials Required\n- **Telegram API** — clinic bot token (all Telegram nodes)\n- **Google Sheets OAuth2** — appointment log\n- **Google Calendar OAuth2** — clinic calendar\n- **Gmail OAuth2** — prescription emails\n- **Slack OAuth2** — error alerts\n\nNever hardcode personal emails, chat IDs, or credential tokens in shared templates."
